{
  "circuit": {
    "description": "Varactor forward-biased: V1=0.5V drives Varactor anode through R=300ohm to ground (cathode). Forward-conduction regime exercises pnjlim limiting on the AK junction and the forward-bias linearised cap formula (Cj = CJO/(1-FC)^(1+M) * (1 - FC*(1+M) + M*Vd/VJ)).",
